---
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>WeightNow Privacy Policy</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Privacy Policy for WeightNow, a watchOS app by Zandar Labs."
    />

    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Zandar Labs" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="WeightNow Privacy Policy" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="WeightNow does not collect personal data. All weight data stays on your device."
    />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://zandarlabs.com/weightnow/privacy" />
    <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary" />

    <link rel="canonical" href="https://zandarlabs.com/weightnow/privacy" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen p-8 bg-[#fdfdfd] font-outfit text-[16px] text-[#4a4d54] max-[640px]:p-4">
    <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl">
      <article class="bg-white rounded-4xl border-[3px] border-dashed border-[rgba(74,77,84,0.11)] overflow-hidden">
        <header class="p-10 border-b-[3px] border-dashed border-[rgba(74,77,84,0.11)] max-[640px]:p-6">
          <img src="/assets/WeightNow.png" alt="WeightNow" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover" />
          <p class="text-[0.85rem] tracking-[0.18rem] uppercase text-[#898b91] font-semibold">WeightNow</p>
          <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.2rem] leading-[1.2] font-semibold tracking-[-0.02rem] max-[640px]:text-[1.8rem]">
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-[#6f7279] leading-[1.7] font-inter">
            Effective date: March 17, 2026
          </p>
        </header>

        <section class="p-10 max-[640px]:p-6">
          <p class="leading-[1.8] font-inter text-[#5c5f66]">
            WeightNow is designed to help you record your weight with privacy in mind. This app does not collect,
            store, or share your personal data.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-[1.3rem] font-semibold">1. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-[1.8] font-inter text-[#5c5f66]">
            We do not collect any personal information, health information, usage analytics, or device identifiers.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-[1.3rem] font-semibold">2. Where Your Data Is Stored</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-[1.8] font-inter text-[#5c5f66]">
            Any weight entries you add in WeightNow are stored locally on your Apple Watch and/or your paired iPhone,
            depending on your device setup. Your data remains under your control on your own device.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-[1.3rem] font-semibold">3. Tracking and Analytics</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-[1.8] font-inter text-[#5c5f66]">
            WeightNow includes no tracking tools, no analytics SDKs, no advertising SDKs, and no third-party telemetry.
            There is no tracking at all.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-[1.3rem] font-semibold">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-[1.8] font-inter text-[#5c5f66]">
            WeightNow does not send your data to external servers or third-party services.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-[1.3rem] font-semibold">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-[1.8] font-inter text-[#5c5f66]">
            If this policy changes in the future, the updated version will be published on this page with a new
            effective date.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-[1.3rem] font-semibold">6. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-[1.8] font-inter text-[#5c5f66]">
            If you have questions about this policy, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@zandarlabs.com" class="text-[#2761f5] underline hover:no-underline">hello@zandarlabs.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
